#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss.rst:138
msgid ""
"Access user-specific preferences for the **Discuss** app by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Manage Users`, select a user, then click "
"the :guilabel:`Preferences` tab."
